{"tid":2022553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"立會黑布抗爭對制度暴力有效嗎？","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T11:52:45.000Z","uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e8b18ddc451ad49d41d7ed4020d80d61c9b8cc","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"令日內會黑布抗爭祇可以是一種象徵式(symbolic)抗爭，象徵式就是你有你解讀人有人解讀。其實要針對就是一個非法內會主持，何不另對起主席台用自家揚聲器宣佈驅逐非法主持。如有保安嘗試武力拉走泛民議員就犯下妨礙公職人員執行公務，要報警及嚴正警告所有保安他們干涉嘅罪行及可被檢控以至私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n手段可能那渣，但要錫身就冇可能應對一個那渣極權。"},{"pid":"f8cd9a4daed9d445ca0d3f6dff8cd286464ee056","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:38:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5873e8bfe52258c9575fdbaa2a0c9d5760cbe6da","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac6844bc3c3da724fe0573c0f130dda6b44114c9","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:41:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87a9030778be754753adcf94b8990938ff1495cd","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a6dcbe021b6274e26df8cc1eea5f8783ec72e54","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"381f5a0e81367d791b207fe6c124efa78509f579","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ek9NSqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fek9NSqC.jpg&h=abad21ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68d48871a0a6dced4bff435e26995a7daeb4060a","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"451649d9149d7172f75cde80ce1ac47e0fbe607f","tid":2022553,"uid":301327,"like":